  "title": "Deputy General Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>We Are Hiring: Deputy General Manager</strong></p><p>We are seeking an experienced and motivated <strong>Deputy General Manager</strong> to support the General Manager in overseeing daily operations and driving business growth. The ideal candidate will have strong leadership skills, strategic thinking, and a proven ability to manage teams and operations effectively.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Assist the General Manager in overall business planning and operations</p></li><li><p>Oversee daily management across departments to ensure efficiency and performance</p></li><li><p>Support strategy development and execution to achieve company goals</p></li><li><p>Manage and coordinate teams, ensuring clear communication and accountability</p></li><li><p>Monitor operational performance and implement improvements</p></li><li><p>Represent the company in internal and external meetings when required</p></li></ul><p><strong>Qualifications:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Bachelor’s degree or above in Business Administration, Management, or a related field</p></li><li><p>Minimum of 2–8 years of management experience, preferably in a similar role</p></li><li><p>Strong leadership, communication, and problem-solving skills</p></li><li><p>Ability to work under pressure and manage multiple priorities</p></li><li><p>Strategic mindset with hands-on execution能力</p></li><li><p>Fluent in English (additional languages are a plus)</p></li></ul><p><strong>What We Offer:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Competitive salary and performance-based incentives</p></li><li><p>Career growth and leadership development opportunities</p></li><li><p>A dynamic and professional working environment</p></li></ul>",
